title: ‘Billions’ S5E11 Recap
description:
Ahead of the ‘Billions’ season finale, The Ringer’s Logan Murdock and Wosny Lambre recap Episode 11, “Victory Smoke.” Logan and Wos break down what happened in the episode, the overarching theme of the season and what predictions they have for characters like Wags, Taylor, and more on the season finale. 
Hosts: Logan Murdock, Wosny Lambre 
Associate Producer: Lani Renaldo
